<pb n="0189a" id="T19.0948.0189a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0189a01" ed="T"/>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<lb n="0189a02" ed="T"/><head type="no">No. 948</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0189a03" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead><note n="0189001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">【原】麗本，【甲】三十帖策子第十七帖，【乙】仁和寺藏古寫本，【丙】嘉保二年寫仁和寺藏本</note>金輪王佛頂要略念誦<note n="0189002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">法＋（通諸佛頂）細註【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0189002"><lem wit="【大】">法</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】【丙】">法<note place="inline">通諸佛頂</note></rdg></app></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0189a04" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0189a05" ed="T"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0189003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔開府…寺〕三十七字【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0189003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔開府…寺〕三十七字<app><lem resp="CBETA.say">－</lem><rdg wit="【大】"></rdg></app>【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app word-count="37" n="0189003"><lem wit="【大】">開府儀同三司特進試鴻臚卿肅國
<lb n="0189a06" ed="T"/>公食邑三千戶賜紫贈司空謚大鑒
<lb n="0189a07" ed="T"/>正號大廣智大興善寺</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0189004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（唐北天竺）＋三【明】，（大興善寺）＋三【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0189004"><lem wit="【大】">三</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">唐北天竺三</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">大興善寺三</rdg></app>藏沙<note n="0189005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">門＋（大廣智）【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0189005"><lem wit="【大】">門</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】">門大廣智</rdg></app>
<lb n="0189a08" ed="T"/>不空奉　詔譯</byline>
<lb n="0189a09" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0189a0901">諸供養儀軌。如<note n="0189006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">餘＝來【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0189006"><lem wit="【大】">餘</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】">來</rdg></app>經中廣說。今但晨暮修
<lb n="0189a10" ed="T"/>行。或四時三時常習不間故。略去重疊簡其
<lb n="0189a11" ed="T"/>要略。行者欲作諸佛頂念誦。先結三部心印
<lb n="0189a12" ed="T"/>及誦真言。加持三業。佛部心印。二手右押左
<lb n="0189a13" ed="T"/>內相叉。二輪並&CB00594;真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0189a14" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0189a1401" type="dharani"><note n="0189007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">唵＋（引一）細註【明】＊</note><app n="0189007"><lem wit="【大】">唵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">唵<note place="inline">引一</note></rdg></app>爾<note place="inline"><note n="0189008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">慈＝惹【明】</note><app n="0189008"><lem wit="【大】">慈</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">惹</rdg></app>以<note n="0189009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">反＝切【明】</note><app n="0189009"><lem wit="【大】">反</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">切</rdg></app>下同</note>曩<note n="0189010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">爾＝&CB00768;【明】【甲】</note><app n="0189010"><lem wit="【大】">爾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】">&CB00768;</rdg></app>翼<note place="inline"><note n="0189011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">去＝二合【明】【甲】【丙】</note><app n="0189011"><lem wit="【大】">去</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】【丙】">二合</rdg></app></note>迦<note place="inline">半<note n="0189012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">音＋（二）【明】＊</note><app n="0189012"><lem wit="【大】">音</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">音二</rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0189a15" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0189a1501">次結蓮華部心印。即前印以左輪屈入掌真
<lb n="0189a16" ed="T"/>言曰。</p>
<lb n="0189a17" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0189a1701" type="dharani"><app source="0189007" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">唵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">唵<note place="inline">引一</note></rdg></app>阿<note place="inline"><note n="0189013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">去＋（聲）【明】＊</note><app n="0189013"><lem wit="【大】">去</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">去聲</rdg></app>引</note>嚕<note place="inline">轉舌引</note>力迦<note place="inline">半<app source="0189012" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">音</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">音二</rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0189a18" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0189a1801">次結金剛部心印。即前佛部心印。屈右輪入
<lb n="0189a19" ed="T"/>掌真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0189a20" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0189a2001" type="dharani"><app source="0189007" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">唵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">唵<note place="inline">引一</note></rdg></app>&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合<note n="0189014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔引〕－【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0189014"><lem wit="【大】">引</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app></note>地力<note place="inline">二合</note>迦<note place="inline">半<app source="0189012" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">音</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">音二</rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0189a21" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0189a2101">次結如來拳印。<note n="0189015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">右＝左【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0189015"><lem wit="【大】">右</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】">左</rdg></app>手蓋光高勝四指。握拳&CB00594;
<lb n="0189a22" ed="T"/>左輪。右手作金剛拳。握左輪甲真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0189a23" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0189a2301" type="dharani"><app source="0189007" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">唵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">唵<note place="inline">引一</note></rdg></app>僕<note place="inline">引</note><note n="0189016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">欠＋（二）細註【明】，欠入＝入欠【丙】</note><note n="0189016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">欠入＝入欠【丙】，欠＋（二）細註【明】</note><app n="0189016"><lem wit="【大】">欠入</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">入欠</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">欠<note place="inline">二</note>入</rdg></app>&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>囉吽<note place="inline">引胸喉中<note n="0189017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">聲＝音【乙】</note><app n="0189017"><lem wit="【大】">聲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">音</rdg></app>如牛<note n="0189018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">吼＋（三）【明】</note><app n="0189018"><lem wit="【大】">吼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">吼三</rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0189a24" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0189a2401">隨誦真言。以印加持自身五處。身器清淨與
<lb n="0189a25" ed="T"/>法相應。便以印加持道場中地。誦真言七遍。
<lb n="0189a26" ed="T"/>其處變成金剛界宮。自然而有眾寶。嚴飾如
<lb n="0189a27" ed="T"/>佛淨土。</p>
<lb n="0189a28" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0189a2801">次結被金剛甲冑護身印。即前佛部心印。二
<lb n="0189a29" ed="T"/>光直&CB00594;頭相拄。屈上節如劍<note n="0189019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔形〕－【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0189019"><lem wit="【大】">形</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app>。二蓋各附二
<pb n="0189b" id="T19.0948.0189b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0189b01" ed="T"/>光背。勿相著。以印加持額上右肩左肩心喉
<lb n="0189b02" ed="T"/>五處。各誦一遍真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0189b03" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0189b0301" type="dharani">唵<note n="0189020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（引）＋一【明】，〔一〕－【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0189020"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">一</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】"><note place="inline">引一</note></rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app>斫羯囉<note place="inline">二<note n="0189021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">合＋（引）【丙】</note><app n="0189021"><lem wit="【大】">合</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">合引</rdg></app></note>&CB02594;<note place="inline">轉舌</note>&CB00069;底<note place="inline">二<note n="0189022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">合＋（二）【明】，（一）【甲】【丙】</note><app n="0189022"><lem wit="【大】">合</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">合二</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【丙】">合一</rdg></app></note>&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0189b04" ed="T"/>捨弭多<note place="inline"><note n="0189023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">二＝三【明】</note><app n="0189023"><lem wit="【大】">二</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">三</rdg></app></note>囉捺囉<note place="inline"><note n="0189024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">三＝二【丙】</note><app n="0189024"><lem wit="【大】">三</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">二</rdg></app>合引</note><note n="0189025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔囉捺囉二合引三〕－【甲】【丙】</note><app n="0189025"><lem wit="【大】">囉捺囉<note place="inline"><note n="0189026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">二合引三＝三合引【乙】</note><app n="0189026"><lem wit="【大】">二合引<note n="0189027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">三＝四【明】</note><app n="0189027"><lem wit="【大】">三</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">四</rdg></app></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">三合引</rdg></app></note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app>跋娑
<lb n="0189b05" ed="T"/>麼<note place="inline">二合</note>攃<note place="inline">倉<note n="0189028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">辣反＝葛切【明】</note><app n="0189028"><lem wit="【大】">辣反</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">葛切</rdg></app></note><note n="0189029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">路＋（引）細註【甲】【乙】，路＝跛【丙】</note><app n="0189029"><lem wit="【大】">路</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">路<note place="inline">引</note></rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">跛</rdg></app>瑟抳<note n="0189030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔二合〕－【丙】＊</note><app n="0189030"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app>灑<note place="inline"><note n="0189031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">四＝五【明】＊</note><note n="0189031" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="＊"/>四＝五【明】＊</note><app n="0189031"><lem wit="【大】">四</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">五</rdg></app></note>囉乞灑<app source="0189030" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">二
<lb n="0189b06" ed="T"/>合</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app>囉乞灑<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00805;<note place="inline">引<note n="0189032" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">五＝六【明】</note><app n="0189032"><lem wit="【大】">五</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">六</rdg></app></note>吽<note place="inline">引</note><note n="0189033" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">發＝撥（普&CB00425;反）【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0189033"><lem wit="【大】">發</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">撥（普&CB00425;反）</rdg></app>吒<note place="inline"><note n="0189034" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔上普&CB00425;反下吒〕－【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0189034"><lem wit="【大】">上普&CB00425;反下吒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app>半音</note>娑
<lb n="0189b07" ed="T"/>&CB00085;<note n="0189035" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔二合引〕－【明】</note><app n="0189035"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">二合引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>賀<note place="inline">引<note n="0189036" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">六＝七【明】</note><app n="0189036"><lem wit="【大】">六</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">七</rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0189b08" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0189b0801">次結迎請聖眾印。二手仰相叉。以二蓋頭相
<lb n="0189b09" ed="T"/>拄如<note n="0189037" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（蓮）＋車【丙】</note><app n="0189037"><lem wit="【大】">車</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">蓮車</rdg></app>輅。隨誦真言。以二輪各撥二光。向
<lb n="0189b10" ed="T"/>身招之或三或七。想諸聖眾乘此車輅來降
<lb n="0189b11" ed="T"/>道場。迎請真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0189b12" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0189b1201" type="dharani">娜麼娑怛&CB00942;<note place="inline">三合轉舌<note n="0189038" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">引＝呼【丙】</note><app n="0189038"><lem wit="【大】">引</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">呼</rdg></app></note>野<note place="inline">一</note>地尾<note place="inline">二合</note>迦南<note place="inline">二</note>薩&CB00085;
<lb n="0189b13" ed="T"/>怛他<note place="inline"><app source="0189013" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">去</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">去聲</rdg></app>引</note>&CB00344;跢<note place="inline">引</note>南<note place="inline">三</note><app source="0189007" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">唵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">唵<note place="inline">引一</note></rdg></app>&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二<note n="0189039" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">合＋（引）【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0189039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">合＋（引）【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】<app><lem resp="CBETA.say">＊</lem><rdg wit="【大】"></rdg></app></note><app n="0189039"><lem wit="【大】">合</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】">合引</rdg></app></note>儗<note place="inline">霓以<note n="0189040" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">反＝切【明】＊</note><app n="0189040"><lem wit="【大】">反</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">切</rdg></app></note>
<lb n="0189b14" ed="T"/>孃<note place="inline">四</note>羯囉灑<note place="inline">二合</note>野娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note n="0189041" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔引五〕－【丙】</note><app n="0189041"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">引五</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0189b15" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0189b1501">次結辦事佛頂印。辟除結界。即前佛部心印。
<lb n="0189b16" ed="T"/>直&CB00594;二光頭相柱。屈上節如<note n="0189042" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">鉤＝&CB00582;【明】，&CB01894;【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0189042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">鉤＝&CB00582;【明】，＝&CB01894;【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0189042"><lem wit="【大】">鉤</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">&CB00582;</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">&CB01894;</rdg></app>。隨誦真言以
<lb n="0189b17" ed="T"/>印頂上左轉三匝。辟除一切不祥諸作障者。
<lb n="0189b18" ed="T"/>便右旋三匝。即成結界辦事真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0189b19" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0189b1901" type="dharani">娜莫三<note place="inline"><app source="0189013" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">去</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">去聲</rdg></app></note>滿多沒馱<note place="inline">引</note>南<note place="inline">一</note>唵吒嚕唵<note place="inline"><note n="0189043" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">三＝二【丙】</note><app n="0189043"><lem wit="【大】">三</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">二</rdg></app><app source="0189039" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">合</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】">合引</rdg></app></note>
<lb n="0189b20" ed="T"/>滿馱娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合<note n="0189044" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔引〕－【丙】</note><app n="0189044"><lem wit="【大】">引</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app></note>賀<note n="0189045" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">引＋（三）【明】，〔引〕－【丙】</note><app n="0189045"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】"><note place="inline">引三</note></rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0189b21" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0189b2101">次結大三昧耶印即前被甲印二。蓋稍開如
<lb n="0189b22" ed="T"/>杵形。以二輪各附二蓋下第一文真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0189b23" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0189b2301" type="dharani"><app source="0189007" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">唵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">唵<note place="inline">引一</note></rdg></app>餉<note place="inline">商障<app source="0189040" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">反</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">切</rdg></app></note>迦<note n="0189046" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">隸＝&CB00942;【明】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0189046" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><app><lem resp="CBETA.Maha">&CB00619;</lem><rdg wit="【大】">隸</rdg></app>＝&CB00942;【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0189046"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00619;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】【乙】">&CB00942;</rdg></app><note place="inline">轉舌<note n="0189047" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">一＝二【明】，〔一〕－【丙】</note><app n="0189047"><lem wit="【大】">一</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">二</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app></note>摩賀<note place="inline">引</note>三<note place="inline"><app source="0189013" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">去</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">去聲</rdg></app></note>麼<note place="inline">鼻<note n="0189048" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔音〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0189048"><lem wit="【大】">音</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app></note>閻
<lb n="0189b24" ed="T"/>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note><note n="0189049" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">賀＋（引三）細註【明】，（引二）【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0189049"><lem wit="【大】">賀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">賀<note place="inline">引三</note></rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">賀引二</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0189b25" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0189b2501">隨誦真言。以印准前右旋三匝。隨行人意遠
<lb n="0189b26" ed="T"/>近。結為大界。</p>
<lb n="0189b27" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0189b2701">次結部母佛眼尊印。二手合掌以二蓋各捻
<lb n="0189b28" ed="T"/>二光背。令如眼<note n="0189050" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">形＝刑【甲】</note><app n="0189050"><lem wit="【大】">形</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">刑</rdg></app>。雙屈二輪入掌真言曰。</p>
<pb n="0189c" id="T19.0948.0189c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0189c01" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0189c0101" type="dharani">娜莫三<note place="inline"><app source="0189013" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">去</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">去聲</rdg></app></note>滿多沒馱<note place="inline">引</note>南<note place="inline">一</note><note n="0189051" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">唵＋（引）細註【明】</note><app n="0189051"><lem wit="【大】">唵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">唵<note place="inline">引</note></rdg></app>嚕嚕<note place="inline">二字皆轉舌</note>娑
<lb n="0189c02" ed="T"/>普<note place="inline">二合</note>嚕<note place="inline"><note n="0189052" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">二＋（合）【丙】</note><app n="0189052"><lem wit="【大】">二</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">二合</rdg></app></note>入&CB00085;<note place="inline"><note n="0189053" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">二＝引【丙】</note><app n="0189053"><lem wit="【大】">二</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">引</rdg></app>合</note><note n="0189054" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">羅＝囉【明】</note><app n="0189054"><lem wit="【大】">羅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">囉</rdg></app>底瑟<note n="0189055" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00062;＝&CB00109;【明】</note><app n="0189055"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00062;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">&CB00109;</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合三</note>悉馱
<lb n="0189c03" ed="T"/>路<note place="inline">引</note>左寧<note place="inline">四</note>薩&CB00085;<note n="0189056" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔引〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0189056"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app>囉他<note place="inline">二合五</note>娑<note place="inline"><app source="0189013" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">去</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">去聲</rdg></app>引</note>馱&CB00576;<note place="inline">寧<note n="0189057" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">頂反＝一切【明】</note><app n="0189057"><lem wit="【大】">頂
<lb n="0189c04" ed="T"/>反</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">一切</rdg></app></note>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合<note n="0189058" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔引〕－【明】</note><app n="0189058"><lem wit="【大】">引</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">&lac;</rdg></app></note>賀<note place="inline"><note n="0189059" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">引＋（六）【明】【甲】【丙】，（六）＋引【乙】</note><app n="0189059"><lem wit="【大】">引</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】【丙】">引六</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">六引</rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0189c05" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0189c0501">次結本尊頂輪王印。即前辦事佛頂印。以二
<lb n="0189c06" ed="T"/>輪並&CB00594;。二蓋平屈兩節頭相<note n="0189060" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">拄＝跓【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0189060"><lem wit="【大】">拄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">跓</rdg></app>。於二輪甲
<lb n="0189c07" ed="T"/>上。結印當心誦真言七遍或一百八遍。又加
<lb n="0189c08" ed="T"/>持身五處各一遍。加持力故。身與本尊合為
<lb n="0189c09" ed="T"/>一體。一字輪王陀羅尼曰。</p>
<lb n="0189c10" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0189c1001" type="dharani">娜莫三<note place="inline"><app source="0189013" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">去</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">去聲</rdg></app></note>滿多母馱<note n="0189061" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">南＋（一）細註【明】</note><app n="0189061"><lem wit="【大】">南</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">南<note place="inline">一</note></rdg></app>勃嚕唵<note place="inline">三<app source="0189039" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">合</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】">合引</rdg></app>嚕字彈舌為一音又引
<lb n="0189c11" ed="T"/>聲從胸喉中出其音如擊大鼓古譯云步林者訛略不正也</note></p>
<lb n="0189c12" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0189c1201">次結獻閼伽<note n="0189062" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔香〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0189062"><lem wit="【大】">香</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app>水印。即前大三昧耶印。以二
<lb n="0189c13" ed="T"/>蓋附著二光背。二輪又安二蓋<note n="0189063" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔側〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0189063"><lem wit="【大】">側</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app>下第一文。
<lb n="0189c14" ed="T"/>如商佉羸盃形。心想印中滿盛香水。舉印額
<lb n="0189c15" ed="T"/>齊。奉獻香水。澡浴本尊及諸聖眾真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0189c16" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0189c1601" type="dharani">娜莫<note n="0189064" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">三＋（去）細註【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0189064"><lem wit="【大】">三</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">三<note place="inline">去</note></rdg></app>滿多沒馱<note place="inline">引</note>南<note place="inline">一</note><app source="0189007" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">唵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">唵<note place="inline">引一</note></rdg></app>遏<note place="inline">轉舌</note>伽<note place="inline"><app source="0189013" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">去</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">去聲</rdg></app></note>囉
<lb n="0189c17" ed="T"/>賀<note place="inline">二合</note>遏伽<note place="inline"><app source="0189013" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">去</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">去聲</rdg></app>二</note><note n="0189065" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">苾＝必【明】</note><app n="0189065"><lem wit="【大】">苾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">必</rdg></app>哩<note place="inline">二合</note>野<note place="inline">三</note>&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>底<note place="inline">丁以
<lb n="0189c18" ed="T"/><app source="0189040" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">反</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">切</rdg></app>引</note>砌<note n="0189066" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">那＋（四）細註【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0189066"><lem wit="【大】">那</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">那<note place="inline">四</note></rdg></app>沫<note place="inline">轉舌</note>儉娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note n="0189067" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">引＋（四）【明】，〔引〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0189067"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】"><note place="inline">引四</note></rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app></p><p id="pT19p0189c1816" place="inline">次結普通供
<pb n="0190a" id="T19.0948.0190a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0190a01" ed="T"/>養印。二手虛心合掌。左右五頂各交上節。想
<lb n="0190a02" ed="T"/>從印流出無量香花飲食宮殿衣服。供<note n="0190001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">養＋（本尊）【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0190001"><lem wit="【大】">養</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">養本尊</rdg></app>及
<lb n="0190a03" ed="T"/>諸聖眾真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0190a04" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0190a0401" type="dharani">娜莫薩&CB00085;沒馱<note n="0190002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔一〕－【明】</note><app n="0190002"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">一</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>冒<note n="0190003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">引＋（一）【明】，〔引〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】＊</note><app n="0190003"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】"><note place="inline">引一</note></rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app>地娑怛&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>南<note place="inline">二</note>
<lb n="0190a05" ed="T"/><note n="0190004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">唵＋（引）細註【明】</note><app n="0190004"><lem wit="【大】">唵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">唵<note place="inline">引</note></rdg></app>薩&CB00085;怛囉<note place="inline">二合三</note>僧<note n="0190005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">去＋（聲）【明】，〔去〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0190005"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">去</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】"><note place="inline">去聲</note></rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app>矩蘇弭跢<note place="inline">引四</note>毘吉孃
<lb n="0190a06" ed="T"/><note place="inline">二合</note>囉<note place="inline">引</note>始&CB00576;<note place="inline">五</note>曩謨娑&CB00418;<note place="inline">二合</note>帝娑&CB00085;<note n="0190006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔二合引〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0190006"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">二合引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app>賀
<lb n="0190a07" ed="T"/><note place="inline">引六</note></p>
<lb n="0190a08" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0190a0801">次結普通佛頂印。即前普供養印稍深交至
<lb n="0190a09" ed="T"/>中節。如花在掌中。修行者若為事緣<note n="0190007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00229;＝忽【明】</note><app n="0190007"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00229;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">忽</rdg></app>速。
<lb n="0190a10" ed="T"/>不能遍結十佛頂印。但結此印誦諸佛頂真
<lb n="0190a11" ed="T"/>言。普通。於修行<note n="0190008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔人〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0190008"><lem wit="【大】">人</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app>亦無過失真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0190a12" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0190a1201" type="dharani">娜莫三<note place="inline"><app source="0189013" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">去</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">去聲</rdg></app></note>滿多母馱<note place="inline">引</note>南<note place="inline">一</note>麼<note place="inline">鼻<note n="0190009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">聲＋（音）【明】，聲＝音【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0190009"><lem wit="【大】">聲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">聲音</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">音</rdg></app></note>&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0190a13" ed="T"/>底賀多舍<note place="inline">引</note>娑<note n="0190010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔上〕－【明】</note><app n="0190010"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">上</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>曩<note place="inline">引</note>南<note place="inline">二</note>唵斫訖囉<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB02594;<note place="inline">轉
<lb n="0190a14" ed="T"/>舌</note>底唵吽<note place="inline">引三</note></p>
<lb n="0190a15" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0190a1501">次誦讚嘆。</p>
<lb n="0190a16" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0190a1601" type="dharani">滿&CB02248;<note place="inline">寧定<note n="0190011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">切＝反【甲】【乙】【丙】＊</note><app n="0190011"><lem wit="【大】">切</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">反</rdg></app>引</note>史抳<note place="inline">尼整<app source="0189040" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">反</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">切</rdg></app>引</note>薩&CB00085;惹<note place="inline">白&CB00256;<app source="0189040" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">反</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">切</rdg></app></note>&CB00753;<note place="inline">言揭<app source="0189040" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">反</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">切</rdg></app></note>地帶
<lb n="0190a17" ed="T"/><note n="0190012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔引〕－【丙】</note><app n="0190012"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app>史抳<note n="0190013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔一〕－【丙】</note><app n="0190013"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">一</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app>拽<note place="inline">延結<app source="0190011" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">切</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">反</rdg></app></note>捨娑尾<note place="inline">二合</note>步<note place="inline">引<note n="0190014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔轉舌〕－【明】</note><app n="0190014"><lem wit="【大】">轉舌</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">&lac;</rdg></app></note>囉步<note place="inline">二
<lb n="0190a18" ed="T"/>合</note>&CB00085;<note n="0190015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔乃〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0190015"><lem wit="【大】">乃</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app><note place="inline">鼻<note n="0190016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">音＋（引）【明】【乙】</note><app n="0190016"><lem wit="【大】">音</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】">音引</rdg></app></note><note n="0190017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">迦＋（二）細註【明】</note><app n="0190017"><lem wit="【大】">迦</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">迦<note place="inline">二</note></rdg></app>滿<note place="inline">引</note>馱吠<note n="0190018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔敷閉反二〕－【明】，敷＝微【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0190018"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">敷閉反<note n="0190019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔二〕－【丙】</note><app n="0190019"><lem wit="【大】">二</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app></note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">&lac;</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】"><note place="inline">微閉反二</note></rdg></app>三<note place="inline"><app source="0189013" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">去</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">去聲</rdg></app></note>麼<note place="inline"><note n="0190020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">鼻＋（音）【明】【丙】</note><app n="0190020"><lem wit="【大】">鼻</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【丙】">鼻音</rdg></app></note>
<lb n="0190a19" ed="T"/>娑多<note place="inline">二合</note>尾&CB00135;也<note place="inline">二合<anchor id="fxT19p0190a07"/>引</note>地跛作訖囉<note place="inline">二合</note>麼<note place="inline"><note n="0190021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">鼻＋（音）【丙】</note><app n="0190021"><lem wit="【大】">鼻</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">鼻音</rdg></app>引</note>
<lb n="0190a20" ed="T"/>里寧<note n="0190022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔三〕－【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0190022"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">三</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app>曩謨娑&CB00418;<note place="inline">二合</note>帝怛囉<note n="0190023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔二合引〕－【丙】</note><app n="0190023"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">二合引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app>怛哩作訖
<lb n="0190a21" ed="T"/>囉<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB02594;<note place="inline">轉舌</note>底<note n="0190024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔丁以反〕－【丙】</note><app n="0190024"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">丁以反</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app>寧<note place="inline">四</note></p>
<lb n="0190a22" ed="T"/><p id="pT19p0190a2201">每念誦先。以五支。或以五相八<note n="0190025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔相〕－【丙】</note><app n="0190025"><lem wit="【大】">相</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app>等觀智。
<lb n="0190a23" ed="T"/>成本尊瑜伽<note place="inline">此法並在頂輪瑜伽極深密一一皆<note n="0190026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔須〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0190026"><lem wit="【大】">須</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app>從灌頂阿闍<note n="0190027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">梨＝黎【明】</note><app n="0190027"><lem wit="【大】">梨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">黎</rdg></app>親<note n="0190028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">受＝授【明】，受＋（之）【丙】</note><app n="0190028"><lem wit="【大】">受</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">授</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">受之</rdg></app></note>或於
<lb n="0190a24" ed="T"/>自身。想布一字安三處<note place="inline">頂舌<note n="0190029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">心＋（也）【丙】</note><app n="0190029"><lem wit="【大】">心</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">心也</rdg></app></note>以字威力能成
<lb n="0190a25" ed="T"/>佛頂輪王尊。又想曼茶<note n="0190030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00256;＝囉【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0190030"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00256;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】">囉</rdg></app>中有香水大海。於
<lb n="0190a26" ed="T"/>海中心有妙高山。七重金山<note n="0190031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">周＝週【明】</note><app n="0190031"><lem wit="【大】">周</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">週</rdg></app>匝圍遶。於妙
<lb n="0190a27" ed="T"/>高頂上有八葉白色蓮華。於一一葉上。右旋
<lb n="0190a28" ed="T"/>布列輪王七寶。所謂金輪象馬珠女兵及主
<pb n="0190b" id="T19.0948.0190b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0190b01" ed="T"/>藏。當前第八葉。想安佛眼尊。十佛頂眷屬前
<lb n="0190b02" ed="T"/>後圍遶。先住此觀已。然後持珠相應念誦。或
<lb n="0190b03" ed="T"/>百或千或至於萬。常功限畢。捧珠頂戴誦部
<lb n="0190b04" ed="T"/>母尊。所有功業願尊守護。又結根本印加身
<lb n="0190b05" ed="T"/>五處。又結普供養印如前供養。又以悅<note n="0190032" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00540;＝喜心【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0190032"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00540;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】">喜心</rdg></app>歌
<lb n="0190b06" ed="T"/>讚本尊。無量悲願攝護我等。令得解脫悉地
<lb n="0190b07" ed="T"/>相應。廣發弘願利樂有情<note n="0190033" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔誓〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0190033"><lem wit="【大】">誓</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app>成正覺。次捧閼
<lb n="0190b08" ed="T"/>伽如前奉獻。又結辦事佛頂印。左旋解界。又
<lb n="0190b09" ed="T"/>結前迎請印。向外撥二中指。誦前真言去羯
<lb n="0190b10" ed="T"/><note n="0190034" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">羅＝囉【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0190034"><lem wit="【大】">羅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】【乙】">囉</rdg></app>灑野句。應云尾薩惹野。即成奉送。又結
<lb n="0190b11" ed="T"/>被甲印誦前真言加身五處。又結三部心印。
<lb n="0190b12" ed="T"/><note n="0190035" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">虔＝處【甲】【丙】</note><app n="0190035"><lem wit="【大】">虔</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【丙】">處</rdg></app>誠作禮發願。<note n="0190036" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">任＝往【明】</note><app n="0190036"><lem wit="【大】">任</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">往</rdg></app>出道場或旋繞經行。轉
<lb n="0190b13" ed="T"/>讀大乘經典。作諸善業以助成就。</p>
<lb n="0190b14" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="close"><jhead><note n="0190037" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（一字）＋金【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0190037"><lem wit="【大】">金</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】">一字金</rdg></app>輪王佛頂要略念誦<note n="0190038" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">法＋（終）細註【明】，乙本奧書曰保安二年孟夏以證本比校了，丙本卷末曰持智手大印處於師子座日輪日蓮臺智拳印所謂金剛拳及成右掘左頭指一節面當心是名智拳印當誦此密言勃魯唵，丙本奧書曰嘉保二年四月二十日於金剛&CB00123;寺奧院書之執筆淳譽</note><app n="0190038"><lem wit="【大】">法</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">法<note place="inline">終</note></rdg></app><note n="0190038" type="rest" place="foot">乙本奧書曰保安二年孟夏以證本比校了，丙本卷末曰持智手大印處於師子座日輪日蓮臺智拳印所謂金剛拳及成右掘左頭指一節面當心是名智拳印當誦此密言勃魯唵，丙本奧書曰嘉保二年四月二十日於金剛&CB00123;寺奧院書之執筆淳譽</note></jhead></juan></div1>
